   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 服务器CouchDb完整部署过程"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## check out git 代码到服务器 (假设docker已经安装好）\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "\n",
    "sudo apt-get install git  \n",
    "git init  \n",
    "git clone http://AlanChaw:binbin1124@github.com/AlanChaw/90024.git  \n",
    "cd 90024/  \n",
    "git checkout origin/Background  \n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 创建CouchDB 数据库并 POST 数据到数据库"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "\n",
    "# create couchdb and push data to couchdb\n",
    "curl -X PUT http://admin:123456@localhost:5984/twitter\n",
    "curl -X POST \"http://admin:123456@localhost:5984/twitter/_bulk_docs \" --header \"Content-Type: application/json\" --data @/home/ubuntu/90024/Background/MyCouchdb/twitter/melb.json\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 安装node.js和grunt"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 下载nodejs源码"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "cd ~  \n",
    "wget https://nodejs.org/dist/v10.15.3/node-v10.15.3-linux-x64.tar.xz   \n",
    "tar xf node-v10.15.3-linux-x64.tar.xz  "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 查看当前版本"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "cd node-v10.15.3-linux-x64/  \n",
    "./bin/node -v  "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 设置软链接"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "sudo ln -s ~/node-v10.15.3-linux-x64/bin/node /usr/bin  \n",
    "sudo ln -s ~/node-v10.15.3-linux-x64/bin/npm /usr/bin  "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 检查"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "node -v\n",
    "npm -v  "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 全局和局部安装grunt\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "cd ~\n",
    "npm install -g grunt-cli\n",
    "PATH=$PATH:$HOME/bin:/home/ubuntu/node-v10.15.3-linux-x64/bin\n",
    "\n",
    "cd /home/ubuntu/90024/Background\n",
    "\n",
    "npm install grunt --save-dev  \n",
    "npm install grunt-cli --save-dev  \n",
    "npm install grunt-couch --save-dev  \n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 编译并提交view"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "grunt couch-compile\n",
    "grunt couch-push"
   ]
  },
